[Bitcoinchain.com](http://bitcoinchain.com/) is informational and analytical resource about crypto currency. We provide you with reliable up-to-date information about [[Bitcoin]] network and a set of analytical tools for monitoring.

Not the whole functional is realized right now.  We have a bunch of brand new bitcoin related ideas, so closely follow updates.

##Features

* [[Mining pool|Bitcoin_Pool]] [[comparison|Comparison_of_mining_pools]] (Found Blocks, Average Hashrate, Luck). Data is taken from pool's API and web sites
* Block List
* Exchange rates in candlestciks and lines (MtGox, BTC-E, Bitstamp) 
* Exchange rates can be compared on a single graph
* User friendly interface, pixel perfect design

